headline: NVR (NVR): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q2 Earnings?
summary: Even though NVR (currently trading at $8,276 per share) has gained 10.3% over the last six months, it has lagged the S&P 500’s 16% return during that period. This may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
